column1: Contents: 1985-1997 Homicide and population data for cities with population of 100,000 and over in 1997
Data source: FBI, Uniform Crime Reports
Note: When jurisdictions did not report, no entry was made for population or the number of homicides.
Please see Table 8 from Crime in the U.S. in the appropriate year for additional information about specific jurisdictions.
These data may differ from earlier versions of this file or from previously published numbers.
